{"tid":105432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好羡慕D可以訓好少既人","createTime":"2017-02-03T01:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T06:39:34.000Z","uid":70912,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6588aafb406685d3e30b96bd964532326f5c87e","tid":105432,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:27:12.000Z","msg":"點解有D人天生可以訓3-4個鐘就夠<br />\n成日見到D咩成功人士既秘笈<br />\n就係唔訓教 或者訓得少 所以時間多<br />\n但我係個種一定要訓7-8個鐘既人<br />\n如果訓唔夠 第二日真係乜都做唔到<br />\n成個人頭暈眼花 個樣好似西迷<br />\n姐係一睇就知未訓醒 全程發牛豆<br />\n飲咖啡都係無用 精神一兩個鐘之後就更加唔舒服<br />\n唔單止身體 精神上同情緒都慢慢變差<br />\n搞到個人勁depress+好大壓力<br />\n然後可能想夜晚睇套戲 或者搵朋友吹水呻下 Relax下咁 拎番少少私人時間<br />\n但原來最後又係惡性循環 搞到訓得3-4粒鐘 每日早起身 又遲放工 唉<br />\n<br />\n究竟係我90後唔挨得<br />\n定係人人都淨係死頂緊<br />\n因為死頂真係唔work令到成個人既狀態更加差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cf8e6a9abb1097c8ef4ced0c1a026ac2e76422","tid":105432,"uid":52024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:28:20.000Z","msg":"我8個鐘都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0c580fb34299e9535f5169dd5bad780cdbd9fa","tid":105432,"uid":17865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:29:21.000Z","msg":"有得揀我都唔想訓得咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返工連搭車都12個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f493f269956b0ed0e114e2c97e3bb7932690c2cd","tid":105432,"uid":32409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:30:01.000Z","msg":"嗰啲可能唔係人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cf56119c17506b48af9dec6cb7ad93151f16a1","tid":105432,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:32:44.000Z","msg":"有D人天生係咁 羨慕唔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識有幾個frd成日都過渡活躍咁永遠都唔會攰 訓得少但仲精神過我<br />\n自己就要訓夠10個鐘先至叫做正常<br />\n以前試過練下挨夜做野不過根本就應付唔到<br />\n個腦攰到完全諗唔到野<br />\n唯有日頭趁精神既時候把握時間專心做野"},{"pid":"8ebc1edfdb21bf6c0ca2a5bb5efde9bdffa4871e","tid":105432,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我8個鐘都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n訓得多反而無咁舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7-8個係完美"},{"pid":"0c6e5baa22b0d6dd383ab6cce741f923eb316c9d","tid":105432,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:35:11.000Z","msg":"好似同基因有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7066cd5f4413a85b7bea727234a70f4e90e049f","tid":105432,"uid":38688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有得揀我都唔想訓得咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返工連搭車都12個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工連搭車13個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd419cefbdbf633a5f9240299eef92e9d2c1d199","tid":105432,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似同基因有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘過智商低真係"},{"pid":"1afbd30e4cb5d500cbd9f5c313694cf851a797e9","tid":105432,"uid":19357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:42:50.000Z","msg":"我要訓8-10個鐘先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4aa8727e20c5d6e4ad769ab09e096e93dfd1745","tid":105432,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:45:09.000Z","msg":"有陣時 做到真係頂唔順<br />\n要夾硬走入toilet<br />\n坐係馬桶訓<br />\n個種辛酸真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fded9282f5f9de31358f8ba3da52de4f9fd094a1","tid":105432,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:46:53.000Z","msg":"傻既，邊有人訓得少會舒服，捱出黎架，捱捱下就慣，至於精唔精神，就係睇下有無方法令自己保持清醒姐。<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過長期每日訓四五個鐘，之後連通兩日宵都頂得住。"},{"pid":"f1cfdfd17b75e53067a5c2e2e029395ff98cec73","tid":105432,"uid":8222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"由細到大都未試過通頂<br />\n前後24小時未訓都未試過"},{"pid":"67e54dde5df6ab78df88d42aa0df31bc82583938","tid":105432,"uid":57442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:49:02.000Z","msg":"我都係要訓夠８- 9個鐘果啲人..放工返到屋企已經差唔多8點, 沖下涼食埋飯已經9點.. 尤其係啲FD 個個都夜一夜先ON..想同佢地打多陣機放鬆下都唔得..次次打到咁上下就話唔打去訓教 搞到好似好掃興咁.."},{"pid":"d0b0a908d0799dc1d8b34f449103985c49331be4","tid":105432,"uid":24648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:52:31.000Z","msg":"天生賤命，瞓多個6個鐘會頭痛"},{"pid":"a9aaa7bc27c35161c5a3113a2d6db170fcdc307e","tid":105432,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻既，邊有人訓得少會舒服，捱出黎架，捱捱下就慣，至於精唔精神，就係睇下有無方法令自己保持清醒姐。<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過長期每日訓四五個鐘，之後連通兩日宵都頂得住。</blockquote><br />\n我知係捱出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係做D routine唔使用腦既野都仲可以頂住唔死 但效率好差真係<br />\n同埋好多時要諗野 對客 Present 開會<br />\n就算你點死撑 但個倦容都會表露出黎<br />\n裝得一時裝唔到成日<br />\n人地一野問 點解呢條友個樣咁唔精神 好似未訓醒咁 都唔知點答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求問 有咩方法可以保持清醒<br />\n姐係唔講人地都唔會知你唔夠訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d827851ac0a6c2f1fae48184f921b34718bd0379","tid":105432,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:55:23.000Z","msg":"捱出黎"},{"pid":"174cf5da1528a13c96d16946751b4e90b2a22f7c","tid":105432,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:56:05.000Z","msg":"晚晚點幾訓<br />\n朝早7點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48cd7e2f52214a585d9f733833901aca5ae21cec","tid":105432,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4def646e0951c1d55799c680d380520f8b6a4b71","tid":105432,"uid":22387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"無話夠唔夠訓<br />\n得時間夠唔夠用姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工時多數訓5-6個鐘<br />\n放假就7-8個鐘"},{"pid":"d9350240ac7d066bf0e2ac82b642e4fc1d55d2d2","tid":105432,"uid":630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:07:48.000Z","msg":"反工連搭車 average 13-14個鐘，每日訓3-4個鐘，每日都好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70fcbb6f659780c93785f4d9e6e04b25185dfc2","tid":105432,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係要訓夠８- 9個鐘果啲人..放工返到屋企已經差唔多8點, 沖下涼食埋飯已經9點.. 尤其係啲FD 個個都夜一夜先ON..想同佢地打多陣機放鬆下都唔得..次次打到咁上下就話唔打去訓教 搞到好似好掃興咁..</blockquote><br />\n你身邊d人早訓焗住你訓都好丫<br />\n最衰係其他人陪你一齊爛癮挨夜 最後辛苦既係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a9287b6b2f9280378c2e3fbd73f8f9ae9131b5","tid":105432,"uid":65775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:11:31.000Z","msg":"唔夠訓真係好辛苦<br />\n有時睡意一黎 就集中唔到<br />\n我都想抵抗 精神d 但係根本唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378de88dcbe3d226f9222bb30c4851bd7de10402","tid":105432,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:11:55.000Z","msg":"我夠每日訓得5個鐘<br />\n又唔見我做成功人士"},{"pid":"406a396faa8ffce259d65b07778a08b648e8bff7","tid":105432,"uid":4756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"有時放假訓勁耐 起身都可以勁攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b858230038c96d38dfb0d2b905e4b5d19008c56d","tid":105432,"uid":13260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"10個鐘都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能因為晚晚發夢 搞到大腦無休息 維持左成2年"},{"pid":"8332a771f8caf3acd167865025187a1bc4810967","tid":105432,"uid":38860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:16:28.000Z","msg":"每日起碼9個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181734954c0824b689e4eca8b7c22dc0cd935a02","tid":105432,"uid":37090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:17:32.000Z","msg":"我要九個鐘先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55507eba80863dbb5c1ff3080bfee06ea6f73471","tid":105432,"uid":81722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:17:48.000Z","msg":"我細個開始已經早睡早起<br />\n到大個即使夜瞓左 差唔多時間起身<br />\n都可以淨係瞓5-6個鐘 然後精神過哂成日<br />\n好多時身邊D朋友一放假個個就瞓十幾粒鐘先起身<br />\n但我放假就可以好早起身 自己一碌木咁唔知做乜鳩<br />\n希望我遲D可以將我呢種特性應用係工作上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e19e01051d06bd9f260f44c1e1c739fc22457e","tid":105432,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:17:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔夠訓真係好辛苦<br />\n有時睡意一黎 就集中唔到<br />\n我都想抵抗 精神d 但係根本唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b630a6215c9e8b67bfc8d9fa509a19af1cd1c3","tid":105432,"uid":33109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:24:28.000Z","msg":"要10-12個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbefbb7ddf60f709d7b2dc5093ac2ff99738497","tid":105432,"uid":14826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:26:32.000Z","msg":"當年長期每晚係沙發訓兩個鐘，返工搭巴士再訓，但星期日一定要補眠，試過無補兩星期，發高燒幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n証明有啲野係要還架"},{"pid":"042de56b75aaf4a2de042ccbc4e0c39b0d59e2b9","tid":105432,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"Same here 唔洗返工訓十幾粒鐘都覺得個人好攰<br />\n應該關睡眠質素事"},{"pid":"23140ed1323c5265fb98d9af3cef8dc61d652672","tid":105432,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔夠瞓就病"},{"pid":"20b59931358552c397985fd4d7696f2e29d6cbd5","tid":105432,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我細個開始已經早睡早起<br />\n到大個即使夜瞓左 差唔多時間起身<br />\n都可以淨係瞓5-6個鐘 然後精神過哂成日<br />\n好多時身邊D朋友一放假個個就瞓十幾粒鐘先起身<br />\n但我放假就可以好早起身 自己一碌木咁唔知做乜鳩<br />\n希望我遲D可以將我呢種特性應用係工作上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要好好感謝老豆老母俾呢個良好基因你<br />\n隨時緊要過俾筆首期你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1586f6d4c48c7ac8a325db3d4c209683c84f60","tid":105432,"uid":2440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:30:03.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔訓到8個鐘以上個人真係攰好多"},{"pid":"268760e002aafcdd63b775f49e291506e5fc6d7c","tid":105432,"uid":25129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"平日一至五返工訓5-6個鐘<br />\n起身果下到洗完面出門口都好無精神，不過行去搭車之後就正常返。<br />\n假期可以訓12個鐘又得，跟返平日訓6個鐘左右又得。<br />\n可能仲後生，所以無乜影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW,終於明白人越大,時間越唔見洗....."},{"pid":"a07ebe778ae5213bfe6b604f46f75040373527ff","tid":105432,"uid":41718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻既，邊有人訓得少會舒服，捱出黎架，捱捱下就慣，至於精唔精神，就係睇下有無方法令自己保持清醒姐。<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過長期每日訓四五個鐘，之後連通兩日宵都頂得住。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相對殘得快"},{"pid":"25c8ba6285bdeee897744296b689ca907f52b5ce","tid":105432,"uid":32161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:41:10.000Z","msg":"其實訓幾耐都唔關事，訓得少又有好精神係取決於睡眠質素"},{"pid":"8dcd5e33adddbddfcb858748af40ed30bb5aed48","tid":105432,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:43:40.000Z","msg":"試下訓4個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507c46f1632fd22643cb3dc99ffbdc9ad14558e2","tid":105432,"uid":71852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"我至少要訓7-8<br />\n訓唔夠個人感覺好虛<br />\n訓得夠個人就好精靈"},{"pid":"459e41d86d954d7c524913a23711220ce127f253","tid":105432,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:55:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實訓幾耐都唔關事，訓得少又有好精神係取決於睡眠質素</blockquote><br />\n如何改善睡眠質素"},{"pid":"d4b196f0052ca6e071a13dd51c70c3700d812f1f","tid":105432,"uid":2550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:58:36.000Z","msg":"打少d丁有幫助"},{"pid":"53deba14a5cfa6a0b10696c269b5315b6bd2ae00","tid":105432,"uid":21309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實訓幾耐都唔關事，訓得少又有好精神係取決於睡眠質素</blockquote><br />\n冇錯 如果訓得好6-7個鐘夠哂"},{"pid":"24af58bc62f24aa49ece7b72adfdf6765c1c414e","tid":105432,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"每日都要訓8個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2e869ed9976d5804cf3efb4065559810ff1bf6","tid":105432,"uid":70877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10個鐘都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能因為晚晚發夢 搞到大腦無休息 維持左成2年</blockquote><br />\n一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚晚都可以發幾個夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2871929690643e606905f234c8f8709f937b79c4","tid":105432,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:21:19.000Z","msg":"有朋友做big4 日日2點幾收第二日又係咁去翻工<br />\n日日訓幾個鐘，星期六日都要翻<br />\n俾著我做一日都頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2f36ef5c8bc9cc66017e649a78d4c8575118b0","tid":105432,"uid":19867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"我都係訓10個鐘先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d00a7f890cd5d37db14ac33bdbf03ed2310a0ff","tid":105432,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似同基因有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘過智商低真係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIndeed"},{"pid":"c936d408b275e9284e2625a80b4c37594c19aae3","tid":105432,"uid":35612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:28:25.000Z","msg":"每日訓多過五個鐘就頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但平時太多時間無乜勢藝 日日虛渡光陰"}]}